body:
You are welcomed by unique in own way company "Prima"! In connection with growth of demand for our services, it is necessary for our firm to expand staff of employees. We require communicative, energetic people, who are capable quickly to adapt oneself to the changing midst. The candidate should easily organize and carry out a set of various administrative duties with ease: from dispatch of the correspondence to the decision of questions of the client. 

If you have a desire to cooperate with us, we request to send your resume here:..... In the resume we also ask you to specify, why just you are right for us.


Working with us you have:

- Career prospects in a rapidly expanding company, professional growth support;
- Involvement in strategic level corporate activities;
- Flexible working schedule;
- Employment contract;
- Part-time job.

Position Requirements: 

- Fluent English, both spoken and written;
- Knowledge of PC: MS Office, typing, messengers;
- Communication skills, ability to communicate freely via phone and e-mail.


Additional Requirements:

- Age 26+;
- USA citizen only; 
- Proactive approach to work;
- Responsiveness;
- Diligence;
- Ethical and honest;
- Communicative;
- Internet.

For immediate consideration, please send resume to: mgorgey@gmail.com
